JavaScript Calculator
---------------------
- Add, subtract, multiply and divide two numbers.
- Clear the input field with a clear button
- Chain mathematical operations together the equal button is hit.
- Correct calculated output

A [Pen](https://codepen.io/mattrelph/pen/aLEYmm) by [Matthew Relph](https://codepen.io/mattrelph) on [CodePen](https://codepen.io).

